fields.title: Deposit DASH to Ripple
fields.description:
So you want to deposit your DASH to Ripple network.

To make it happen, please follow these steps:

  1. Add trust to the {gateway_ripple_address} (it's important to receive funds);
  2. Provide your Ripple address and desired amount in the box, click the "Start" button;
  3. We will provide a Dash address for you.
    Please send your DASH to that address.
    Also, you will be given a link to your transaction, where you can check its current status.

Please note that our gateway will not wait forever, make sure you send your funds in {transaction_expiration_minutes} minutes after starting.

fields.title: Withdraw DASH from Ripple
fields.description:
So you want to withdraw your DASH from Ripple network to a DASH address.

To make it happen, please follow these steps:

  1. Provide your Dash address and desired amount in the box, click the "Start" button;
  2. We will provide our Ripple address and a unique destination tag for you.
    Please send your Ripple DSH tokens to that address with the destination tag.
    Also, you will be given a link to your transaction, where you can check its current status.

Please note that our gateway will not wait forever, make sure you send your funds in {transaction_expiration_minutes} minutes after starting.
